node.text:
Nothing like a Trader Joe’s haul to kick start the week. I don’t know if it’s just me but there is something so satisfying about making a Trader Joe’s run— it never feels like a chore! 😋

I put together a fun surprise that I’m going to give 3 of you! Just comment & let me know your ride or die Trader Joe’s goodies to enter.
#groceryhaul #traderjoes #groceryshopping #traderjoesfinds #traderjoeshaul

node.text:
Kicking Monday off with an easy, fresh + glowy makeup look 🙌🏽 I also use a few of my fave drugstore finds. What do you want to see next? 

PRODUCT BREAKDOWN:
+ Tula : Sunscreen and filter primer (code COURTNEY) 
+ Armani Luminous Silk Foundation : 7.5 (a bit dark for me right now)
+L’Oreal Glotion : 903 (used in video) or 904 (for more of a tan) 
+ Patrick Ta Blush : She’s that girl 
+ Too Faced Bronzer : Sunbunny 
+ Lancôme Juicy Tube : Miracle
+ Wet N Wild Highlight : Golden Flower Crown 
+ Mascara Cocktail : Lancôme CILS BOOSTER, Essence Lash Princess, Lancôme Lash Idole http://liketk.it/3g03t #liketkit @liketoknow.it

node.text:
Who are you consuming in real life & on social media? Because it is most definitely consuming you (for better or worse). That includes YOURSELF! ✨🙌🏽

How’s your self-talk? 💗 How are you? Your heart, your head. It’s the beginning of a new month, a great time for a fresh start and a little check-in. Do you build yourself up, encourage, give grace, speak highly of yourself in your head? It matters. Confidence starts with the belief in yourself and that starts with your ability to keep the promises you make to yourself. 
Just a little reminder that you are a badass and you got this, whatever “this” is. 🤜🏽🤛🏽

http://liketk.it/30TwV #liketkit @liketoknow.it

node.text:
Nothing like a Trader Joe’s haul to kick start the week. I don’t know if it’s just me but there is something so satisfying about making a Trader Joe’s run— it never feels like a chore! 😋

I put together a fun surprise that I’m going to give 3 of you! Just comment & let me know your ride or die Trader Joe’s goodies to enter.
#groceryhaul #traderjoes #groceryshopping #traderjoesfinds #traderjoeshaul

Let’s talk summer reads! 🐬🦀☀️ Are you an old school book or kindle person? I’m a real book kinda girl (I love the feel and SMELL! Is that weird? lol)

I’m very into reading this summer and wanted to put together a list of YOUR top recs as well as the 5 I bought to read ASAP 📚 . Side note, I just started “The Midnight Library” and it’s so good!! Anyone want to read it with me? 

5 books to read this summer: 

+ The Midnight Library by Matt Haig
+ The Paradise Series by Elin Hilderbrand
+ Malibu Rising but Taylor Jenkins Reid
+ The Seven Husband’s Of Evelyn Hugo by Taylor Jenkins Reid 
+ The Alchemist by Paulo Coelho 

Swipe to see the full list! & save this post for all the best summer reads. Did I forget any MUSTS? 💛 @liketoknow.it #liketkit http://liketk.it/3jyTl
